Definition: defend, explain, clear away, or make excuses for by reasoning
Example: rationalize the child's seemingly crazy behavior; he rationalized his lack of success
Synonyms: apologise, noun, communication, apology, excuse, adj, all, excusatory, rationalize, cognition, rationalization, rationalise, rationalisation, defend, explain, clear, away, or, make, excuses, for, by, reasoning, the, child, s, seemingly, crazy, behavior, he, rationalized, his, lack, of, success
Frame: 8
Category: verb.communication
